\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Hello my name is Ksera, I am a member of the new faction of ascended, by concertrating the power from thousands of our people into one idiviual, that indivivual is able to unlock their inner potential and become like me an asceded, our former enemies are destroyed, we where able to master this ritual and a number of the priesthood became ascended, and we were able to destroy the enemy attacking us, this should have been a moment of celbration for our people, we have become something more we where, unforently this is not the case, power corrupts an indidivual and the leader of the preists Zvera }
