\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Zvera was able to control the majority of those that become ascended, in his thoughts ascendent powers was to much for the general population and should be restricted, I oposed him, but I was alone I this effort, Zvers started by destroying most of our cities and temples and stopping anyone ele from becoming ascended}
